# IdentityDocumentWebPresentmentRawRequest.RequestType

**Enumeration**

Defines the types of request formats supported by the system.

## Declaration

```swift
enum RequestType
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **IdentityDocumentWebPresentmentRawRequest.RequestType.iso18013MobileDocument**: Corresponds to the request format defined in ISO 18013-7.

## Conforms To

- Copyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
